/target
**/*.rs.bk
*.pdb
.env
*.log
.DS_Store
/dist
/.build-tools
node_modules/
.wrangler/
# Local caches — cloned upstream sources we consult but don't ship.
# `.cache/lucide-upstream/` is a shallow clone of lucide-icons/lucide;
# see crates/shelldeck/assets/icons/lucide/README.md for how we pick
# icons out of it.
/.cache/
# Logo exploration / prototypes — production assets live in assets/images/brand/
/crates/shelldeck/assets/images/logo-concepts/
# Obsidian vault metadata — local notes tooling, not part of the repo.
/.obsidian/
# Claude Code local runtime state (locks, etc.) — not project content.
/.claude/*.lock
